quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"[Prophet], have you considered the person who denies the Judgement"
  107,2,It is he who pushes aside the orphan
  107,3,and does not urge others to feed the needy
  107,4,So woe to those who pray
  107,5,but are heedless of their prayer
  107,6,those who are all show
  107,7,and forbid common kindnesses